{% extends "layouts/base.twig" %}

{% block content %}
<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-between p-24 bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-900 transition-colors duration-150">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold dark:text-white">About</h1>
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <p class="mb-4">
            JSON Formatter Live is a simple, fast, and free online tool to format and beautify your JSON data.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
            This tool was created to provide a lightweight, browser-based solution for developers who need to quickly format JSON data without installing any software.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
            Features include:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-8 mb-4">
            <li>Format JSON with proper indentation</li>
            <li>Minify JSON to reduce size</li>
            <li>Syntax highlighting</li>
            <li>Error detection</li>
            <li>Dark mode support</li>
            <li>Keyboard shortcuts</li>
            <li>Copy to clipboard functionality</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            The source code for this project is available on <a href="https://github.com/alexandrunastase/json-formatter-live" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
